citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2;50 PM on
20-NOV-18.
Knocked on door and rang bell with no answer. Called contact phone number and left message. No one visible on
property. Waited 30 minutes. Licensee returned call that evening.
